		Notes=$begin_cdata$(23-July-2011)

This project uses HFSS "Solver on Demand" to 
run full-wave electromagnetic analysis and calculate
differential s-parameters from the via transition in the
frequency range 0-10 GHz.

The antipad diameter can be changed by modifying
the project variable $antiPad. $end_cdata$
